ick - its free (no mana).</P><P>Glonoin - A Necromancer not named Sue ( or Sally :) )</P><P>Using your dead bodies to create a better tomorrow..<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
