u can pull at less HP/Mana than you normally would, since you only need to expend mana using darkness on the mob, and can recover hp/mana while your pet kills the mob, thus being efficient even in what would otherwise be downtime.</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
