        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Well, personaly I like my "wanabe duckstaff" as my mage friend calls it.  Here is an example where it kicks Invoke Fear's ass.  A 57 gmage (with epic)  and I (56 gnecro) were following around with mobs in  Western Wastes.  I can chained Yeldema while pets ripped him a new one.  Start fear off with normal invoke then mash click with the staff.  The two pets made short work of the dragon.  <BR>So we've been looking around for mobs that 2 people shouldn't be able to kill, in fear kite safe zones.  There are about 4 dragons we found we could take down (we pulled them all into the water to avoid add's)  </P><P>Also if your going to try the Bulthar Herdleader in CS you need this staff, he breaks fear so often and can't be snared, real nightmare when he turns your pet inside out.</P><P>Well, anyhow  I love my staff, paid 10k for it on the Brell server.  Now with all the pet changes I personal think it's worth far more than what I paid for it.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
