        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Well I have to admit as this stick's strongest supporter I sold mine today.  Couldn't resist, someone was watching me chain whack HGs in Rathe Mnts and dropped 20k in cash on my HG pharming butt.  Only stipulation in the deal was that if I ever wanted it back and had 22k (10% markup) he would give it back.  </P><P>Took me all of 10 minutes to start missing it, when I went to farming SGs in Oasis for Essence of Sunlights.  a. had to mem Invoke Fear, and b. had to actually use mana to fear kite (besides the customary dooming darkness)</P><P>Two things I noticed - 1. if you cast another spell first (ie. Dooming Darkness) it takes 3 seconds to refresh your buttons, then another 3 seconds to cast Invoke Fear = 6 seconds for the first cast of fear.  The spell isn't any faster than the stick, assuming you cast darkness before fearing (a given, lest your fear kited mob take off at full speed) and 2. when you are chain killing stuff and cast fear two or three times apiece, that 300 mana per kill adds up FAST.  Four kills in rapid succession at 3 fears apiece is 1200 mana, the difference between being at 80m at the end of that rampage and being 20m (or OOM).</P><P>And it looks so cool.  I am almost ashamed to be seen with a beer mug of moggok and a book.</P><P>Go forth, be proud.  And enjoy your stick.</P><P>Glonoin</P><P>Using your dead bodies to create a better tomorrow..<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
